WEBVTT

00:00.233 --> 00:04.103
<i>Previously on "Blood drive"...</i>

00:03.491 --> 00:04.623
You okay?

00:04.625 --> 00:06.592
I may have triggered
a tracking device.

00:06.594 --> 00:07.860
<i>Go find Arthur.</i>

00:07.862 --> 00:09.762
<i>Make Heart pay
for what they've done.</i>

00:09.764 --> 00:13.165
Relax.
Put the cop act to rest.

00:13.167 --> 00:15.534
<i>Or are you afraid
you might just like</i>

00:15.536 --> 00:17.870
this little paradise
I've created?

00:17.872 --> 00:19.738
I felt like you had my back,

00:19.740 --> 00:21.640
like you were willing
to go dark with me.

00:21.642 --> 00:23.542
What the hell's
a soul reclamator?

00:23.544 --> 00:24.743
Sooner or later,

00:24.745 --> 00:26.512
the good cop
is gonna have to admit...

00:26.514 --> 00:28.547
He's a bad guy.

00:28.549 --> 00:30.716
<i>I'll save your pathetic
little lives</i>

00:30.718 --> 00:33.852
if you agree to go on one last
adventure with me.

00:33.854 --> 00:35.521
You get to get to the bottom

00:35.523 --> 00:37.656
<i>of this bizarre obsession
they have</i>

00:37.658 --> 00:39.825
<i>with you and your sister.</i>

00:43.631 --> 00:44.630
<i>You're not gonna answer?</i>

00:44.632 --> 00:46.465
<i>Don't do this to me.</i>

00:46.467 --> 00:48.434
<i>- It's a simple question.
- It's not.</i>

00:48.436 --> 00:49.835
- Favorite movie.
- I don't... I don't know.

00:49.837 --> 00:51.036
What do you mean,
you don't know?

00:51.038 --> 00:52.438
I don't know.
I don't...

00:52.440 --> 00:53.472
I-I don't watch any movies.

00:53.474 --> 00:54.573
What are you talk...

00:54.575 --> 00:55.774
Give me something.

00:55.776 --> 00:56.975
Um, uh, okay, here.

00:56.977 --> 00:59.044
Super easy.
Dogs or cats?

00:59.046 --> 01:00.679
Cats.

01:00.681 --> 01:02.614
Definitely cats.

01:03.884 --> 01:05.050
What do you have against dogs?

01:05.052 --> 01:06.218
Nothing. I...

01:06.220 --> 01:07.553
Look, I had a dog growing up.

01:07.555 --> 01:09.588
I had a black lab named Daisy.

01:09.590 --> 01:12.958
She was great,
but she hated Karma.

01:12.960 --> 01:16.462
She would growl at her,
and then one day, bam!

01:16.464 --> 01:17.963
She bit Karma right here.

01:17.965 --> 01:19.698
Pinned her down.

01:19.700 --> 01:21.467
She was only ten.

01:21.469 --> 01:22.468
Jesus.

01:22.470 --> 01:23.669
I wasn't there,

01:23.671 --> 01:24.837
but the neighbors saw it,
thank god,

01:24.839 --> 01:27.573
and pulled her off,
called the cops.

01:27.575 --> 01:30.676
They were coming
to put her down.

01:30.678 --> 01:32.878
Look, I knew it had
to happen, but...

01:32.880 --> 01:34.746
She was my dog,

01:34.748 --> 01:37.249
and I wasn't gonna let anyone
lay a hand on her.

01:37.251 --> 01:41.653
So I took her out to the quarry.

01:45.892 --> 01:47.025
Guess that's the first time

01:47.027 --> 01:49.962
I had to kill to protect Karma.

01:49.964 --> 01:53.031
Who'd have thought that'd become
my whole life, huh?

01:53.033 --> 01:55.000
What a lovely story,
but I was really hoping

01:55.002 --> 01:56.602
the "world's
greatest sister" bit

01:56.604 --> 01:57.970
would've ended
after Karma croaked.

01:59.740 --> 02:01.273
Asshole.
Succubus!

02:01.275 --> 02:02.708
It's not worth it.

02:02.710 --> 02:05.077
After today,
we're free and clear.

02:05.079 --> 02:06.612
Just one last little thing,

02:06.614 --> 02:07.980
and then we're done
with this asshole.

02:07.982 --> 02:09.047
Forever.

02:09.049 --> 02:10.749
Don't miss the turn.

02:11.752 --> 02:13.085
All right, coming through!

02:21.595 --> 02:23.695
If you try to run,

02:23.697 --> 02:25.931
the guards have orders
to shoot you down.

02:25.933 --> 02:28.700
Trust me, you won't want
to miss this.

02:28.702 --> 02:30.669
Run from what?

02:30.671 --> 02:31.970
Pull it through!

02:31.972 --> 02:34.673
Tonight we go live,
and I'm gonna put on

02:34.675 --> 02:37.009
the greatest show this crumbling
shit pile of a planet

02:37.011 --> 02:38.744
has ever seen.

02:38.746 --> 02:40.312
After tonight,

02:40.314 --> 02:42.080
he can't hurt us anymore.

